OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784722711
OL,3,CInflation falls to 2.6% as food and
OL,4,Cfuel prices drop in 15-month low
OL,6,FUK inflation fell to the lowest rate
OL,7,Fin 15 months in June as food and fuel
OL,8,Fprices dropped, in what could be an
OL,9,Fearly boost to new prime minister Andy
OL,10,FBurnham's cost of living focused
OL,11,Fgovernment.
OL,13,FThe rate of Consumer Prices Index
OL,14,F(CPI) was 2.6% in June, down from 2.8%
OL,15,Fin May, according to the Office for
OL,16,FNational Statistics (ONS).
OL,18,FThis was the lowest level since March
OL,19,F2025, and also came in below the 2.7%
OL,20,Frate that most economists had been
OL,21,Fexpecting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
