OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784722711
OL,3,CInflation falls to 2.6% as food and
OL,4,Cfuel prices drop in 15-month low
OL,6,FONS chief economist Grant Fitzner
OL,7,Fsaid: "A fall in motor fuel prices,
OL,8,Fparticularly diesel, helped ease
OL,9,Finflation in June.
OL,11,F"Food prices fell this month, driven
OL,12,Fby products including chocolate,
OL,13,Fmargarine and beef.
OL,15,F"Clothing prices also fell with the
OL,16,Fstart of summer sales, with bigger
OL,17,Fdiscounts than last year.
OL,26,@oD@GOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
