CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784722711
OL,3,CInflation falls to 2.6% as food and
OL,4,Cfuel prices drop in 15-month low
OL,6,F"The cost of raw materials dipped for
OL,7,Fthe first time since January, mainly
OL,8,Fdue to the lower price of crude oil,
OL,9,Fwhile the increase in the costs of
OL,10,Fgoods leaving factories slowed again."
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FNewly appointed Chancellor John Healey
OL,18,Fsaid: "Falling inflation is news
OL,19,Ffamilies want to hear, but there is
OL,20,Fmuch more to do to give people the
OL,21,Fbreathing space they need.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@fO]zD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
