FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784722711
OL,3,CInflation falls to 2.6% as food and
OL,4,Cfuel prices drop in 15-month low
OL,6,F"That is why yesterday we cut VAT on
OL,7,Felectricity bills, and today we're
OL,8,Fannouncing a #2 cap on bus fares from
OL,9,FJanuary.
OL,11,F"We have chosen to focus on the cost
OL,12,Fof living in our first week,
OL,13,Fsignalling that concern for working
OL,14,Fpeople will be at the heart of
OL,15,Feverything we do.
OL,17,F"Both these changes are a win-win.
OL,18,FThey help keep inflation down while
OL,19,Fhelping people afford the essentials."
